<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rapier" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rapier,</orth> a small sword used in thrusting: <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.84" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 84</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 4, 61</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.61" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 4, 61</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.13" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 13</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.183" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.183" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 183</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.258" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 258</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.258" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 258</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r2 4.40" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 IV, 40</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.4.215" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 4, 215</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 2.1.60" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 1, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.3.37" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 3, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.4.80" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 80</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 1, 54</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 4.2.85" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.5.57" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 5, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 4.3.57" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.359" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 359</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.1.10" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. oth 5.1.2" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. V, 1, 2</bibl>. <cit><quote>the Frenchman hath good skill in his r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.231" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. II, 1, 231</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I do excel thee in my r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 78</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>gave you such a masterly report for your r.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 99</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the r. and dagger man,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 4.3.15" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. IV, 3, 15</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what's his weapon? R. and dagger,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.152" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 152</bibl></cit>. <emph>six French --s and poniards,</emph> 156 (cf. <emph>Dagger</emph>).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>